the 16th of April, has anyone got any info. for that date yet?  He wouldn't  
say what it is, last date he gave was for Valentine's Day, and that day was 
went  Egypt started it's uprising, around time the pale horse was seen going 
through  the crowd, on camera and disappeared, the news claims it was not a 
hoax, and  other's saw it too. sf.
